GAS BURNING FIREPLACE LOCATED IN THE FAMILY ROOM WHICH OVERLOOKS THE KITCHEN. LOVELY BREAKFAST AREA WITH DOUBLE WINDOW. KITCHEN HAS ALL NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES TO INCLUDE A DOUBLE REFRIGERATOR GRANITE COUNTERTOPS THROUGHOUT. WASHER/DRYER CONNECTIONS LOCATED ON THE MAIN LEVEL ALONG WITH HALF BATH AT ENTRANCE. STAIRCASE HAS ALSO BEEN RENOVATED TO EXCLUDE CARPET. THIS HOME WILL NOT LAST WITH ALL UPGRADES INCLUDING MASTER AND 1/2 VANITY BEING COMPLETELY UPDATED. PLEASE GO SHOW!
